title: THE BOYS Season 2 Episode 5 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: I think Mave wants The Deep to get the flight recorder from last season’s Airline crash at the  bottom of the ocean to get Homelander.
Butcher giving commands to Terror to fluff on his toy was probably my favorite part of that episode
Adele is Stormfront’s daughter (that wasn’t born with powers) and has aged normally since being born in the 40s or something... I’m calling it now.
I was expecting Homelander to stop caring about his public image after the last episode of him realizing he only needs himself. But I guess he still needs to be loved apparently?
Dude that Katie Couric interview!!! It was a perfect jab at  the whole Tom Cruise and Katie Holmes Scientology marriage interview! Hilarious!
description:
In this video we take a deep dive and breakdown episodes 5 of Amazon's THE BOYS Season 2. Review, recap, and easter eggs!
